49
00:01:35,950 --> 00:01:37,550
When you multiply it by 1 to 6,

50
00:01:38,060 --> 00:01:39,860
the set of digits stays the same,

51
00:01:40,110 --> 00:01:41,759
the sequence doesn't change,

52
00:01:41,759 --> 00:01:42,800
ولا يزال

53
00:01:43,229 --> 00:01:44,539
تلك الأرقام الستة نفسها.

54
